_sText:
**zm Inside The Fortress final** - 
I think it will be the last version of my map, some things have changed, such as Skybox, sounds and some textures.
More spots were created, and more secrets to discover.
Added ambient sound.
The map is now darker than the previous version, map lights won another highlight.
There are 64 slots, but I think it will lag the server with so many people.

Have fun - Kill the zombie
